Work Order Estimation

Service agents and other users can give customers accurate quotes for field service tasks prior to the creation of work orders. Boost user efficiency and customer satisfaction with a user-friendly guided flow that considers asset details, warranties, and service contract entitlements.

Estimate Field Service Work Before You Create Work Orders
Improve customer satisfaction by enabling your users to provide your customers with a quote and an estimate of the work to be done associated with a specific asset. Users can generate quotes for assets based on work types and necessary products. They can also apply discounts from associated coverages.

Estimate Field Service Work and Quote Costs to Customers Easily
title: Work Order Estimation in Salesforce
